<div class="col five-sm clear">
<h2 id="section-top">Overview</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="news-teaser">
<div class="panel panel-nonedit module">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<p><a href="#news-title">News:</a></p>
<ul><li>Our latest news </li></ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContentab05ed70f5ef4768b932c1aa2fdf20f1">
</div>
<p>Leeds Community Healthcare NHS Trust provide a range of community-based health services across the Leeds area and offer high quality healthcare in the most appropriate setting for our patients, whether that is in their own home, a local health centre, or a community hospital.</p>
<p>For more information please visit <a href="http://www.leedscommunityhealthcare.nhs.uk">www.leedscommunityhealthcare.nhs.uk</a> or follow us on twitter <a href="https://twitter.com/lchnhstrust?lang=en">@LCHNHSTrust</a> or like our Facebook page, <a href="https://en-gb.facebook.com/LeedsCommunityHealthcare/">@LeedsCommunityHealthcare</a></p>
<p> </p></div>
</div>
</div>
